Thankfully I was so relaxed right from the beginning, as Dr Poonam had explained the whole procedure to me ..Her calm caring demeanour .. her warm friendliness..her expert touch was so comforting ..Dr Siddharth  , with his gentle touch and expertise too, also kept me from feeling any pain ..something I was really scared of !!...They were ably assisted by Harish ..
I was so impressed with the cleanliness and sterilisation process in the clinic ...
I have been very fortunate to get treated here ..Thank you so much Dr Poonam , Dr Siddharth .. and Harish ..🙏🏻God bless you all ..🙏🏻

Dr. Poonam Dutt is an excellent dentist. She did my cleaning and cavities with utmost care concern and to perfection. I strongly reccomend her to everyone who was a mix of warmth and professionalism. She is an ace dentist and I have been going to her for last 25 years. 
Thankyou Dr Poonam Dutt for always giving me the best.
Shabnam Chatterjee

Excellent annual teeth cleanings for 8 years! As a professor and a practitioner, ** **** *** **** ********* ** *** ****** ****** *********** She uses the same advanced equipment as my former dentist in New York and her technique is thorough yet careful to minimize pain. Last but not least, she makes time to answer all my dental hygiene questions!

I had an amazing experience with Dr. Poonam Dutt. Initially I was really scared of the pain that I might have while the tooth was extracted. But she did it very carefully and so well that I did not feel the pain. Besides she is very polite and she listens to your problem with patience.

I found Synergy to have a highly professional set up, Dr Poonam being a comforting figure. She gave me extensive pre and post procedure consultation and all my procedures took place hassle free.
The attendant Mr Harish is easy to approach and sincere.

Had a very delightful and satisfying experience. Resolved our dental problems with professional competence and patience.  Dr Poonam Dutt is a doctor with a humane touch. The staff is also very responsive and helpful. Covid regulations are all followed.

*** ****** **** ** * ***** ******** The way she explained the issue to me was very clear. Her friendliness and reassuring attitude make me less fearful of the problem. I have had three sittings with her and I am extremely satisfied. I would definitely recommend her to family and friends.

A most professionally run clinic by Dr Poonam Dutt who is extremely  proficient and her wholesome experience is evident in the treatment. The staff is competent and very courteous. It is so reassuring to see and undergo the highest standards of hygiene and sanitation in these times of pandemic. Very impressed and satisfied with the entire experience. Thank you Dr Poonam Dutt.

Dr Poonam Dutt delivers her expertise with a personal touch; it is this balance  that brings me back to her for needful treatment. She has been treating me post maxillofacial surgery during Nov, 2011. Till mid of year 2015, i was based at Delhi, but even now I visit her from Bangalore when required - average 2 times a year.

I reached the clinic with excruciating pain in my teeth and  left with no pain, all within an hour. Dr. Dutt is a thorough professional and incredibly friendly. Moreover, I appreciate the fact that she prioritises the patient and she chose to suggest dental fillings as treatment instead of suggesting root canal therapy at the outset. I would definitely recommend Dr. Dutt for dental procedures and consultation.
